title: Dinosaurs - Pacifica
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Vietnamese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has several vegan choices including a crispy shredded tofu sandwich with vegenaise, a roasted portobello sandwich, a tofu and taro salad and a vegan spring roll. Some juices and shakes are vegan as well. Basic sandwich shop with tables and chairs and a casual atmosphere.
